  </div>




</a></div>
    
  <div class="teaser-date">04/30/24</div>
  <h4 class="teaser-headline">
      <a href="/article/machine-learning-and-theory?language_content_entity=und" rel="bookmark"><span>Machine learning and theory</span>
</a>
  </h4> 
  <p>Theoretical physicists use machine-learning algorithms to speed up difficult calculations and eliminate untenable theories—but could they transform what it means to make discoveries?</p>

</article>

<article class="node node--type-article node--view-mode-teaser">

